title: Jadyn's 20th Birthday
description: Your 20th Birthday. I loved this day because it was my way of showing how much you meant to me. It was also memoric because it was your first introduction to some of my friends.

title: Jadyn’s Day
description: This day was all about you. You deserved to have every light shine on you, and seeing you glow while experiencing your dream day was something I’ll never forget.

title: Where it all Began
description: A leap of faith I took. Little moments that felt like the end of the world to me. I am so happy this day happened.

title: Gift exchange
description: After Christmas break we met for some gift exchanges. I still absolutely loved the cookies!

title: LEGOS
description: Another day together. We built the legos I got you for christmas. This day was special!

title: Best day of my Life
description: A long day with lots of moments. Some loud, some quiet. All of them worth keeping. This day you made it for me. I never felt so special and seen in my life. Thank you for this.

title: Photoshoot You didn't want to do
description: I was like take some flicks with me. You absolutely didn't want to but still did anyways. I look back at these often because it was fun.

title: FLOWERSSSS
description: A day packed with moments. I bought you flowers for the very first time. We went on a hangout(not a date). I remember this day so vividly because I was so happy to get you flowers.

title: February Begins
description: Starting February together. A lot of pictures, from pottery to making homemade pizza. I definitely loved this day.

title: Dancing in the Rain
description: A item off the bucket list.

title: Eyebrows
description: You absolutely ate down on my eyebrows. This was the first memory of when you started getting comfy picking at my face. I still don't mind to this day.

title: Valentine’s Day
description: Valentine’s Day — a day full of love, warmth, and quiet moments that meant everything to me.

title: Soft Days
description: Date night.

title: 3am Shenanigans
description: You came back from the club to me locking in for my physics exam. I aced it!

title: The Day I Asked You
description: The day I asked you to be my girlfriend. One of the most important days of my life — choosing you, officially.

title: My First Letter
description: The first letter you wrote for me.

title: Letting Go
description: Picnic date where we let the things that bothered us go.

title: Meeting Your Family
description: The first time I met your family and visited your home. Such a special trip — full of nerves, laughter, and moments that made everything feel even more real. I loved getting to see where you come from.

title: Locking In & Goofing Around
description: A fun day of locking in, being productive, and still finding time to goof around together. One of those days that felt easy and comfortable.

title: First Time Doing Your Nails
description: The first time I ever did your nails. I still don’t think I did that great, but you let me try anyway — and that meant everything.

title: Walks & Laying in the Grass
description: We went on a walk and laid in the grass together. You looked so beautiful that day — one of those quiet moments I’ll never forget.

title: Koi Pond & the Hut
description: We went to the koi pond on campus and found a little man-made hut. It was a hard day emotionally, but we still made something meaningful out of it together.

title: Clara’s Birthday
description: It was Clara’s birthday. You looked absolutely amazing. Marissa needed me that night, and I still feel bad because I wanted to give you all my attention and make it a perfect night for you.

title: Betty’s Noodles Date
description: We went on a date to Betty’s Noodles. I also did a full photo shoot of you just because — one of my favorite things to do.

title: Easter & the Cutie Basket
description: Easter time. I surprised you with a cutie basket and we went to your home to celebrate. This was when I really started to feel like I had another family.

title: Parents Day & Becoming One With Nature
description: Parents Day for AY. Sonya came up, we had a coffee date, and spent time outside together — becoming one with nature.

title: Gobi’s & the Movies
description: We had a date at Gobi’s and then went to the movies. I loved the little hat you wore — one of those nights that just felt warm and easy.

title: Powderpuff Training
description: We were training for powderpuff, and let me tell you — YOU’RE A DOGGGG. Watching you go all out was insanely attractive.

title: Living Outside
description: We spent the day outside laying in the grass, just living. Moments like these always felt special to me — quiet, simple, perfect.

title: Beach Day & Ice Cream
description: We went to the beach and got ice cream. You were so cute when you asked me to take a picture of you on the rock. I love you so much.

title: Three Months
description: We had a late night celebration of our three month anniversary — goofing off, talking about our fits, and just enjoying each other.

title: Golf Cart Adventures
description: We took a trip to your home and you were whipping that golf cart like a pro. One of those days that felt carefree and fun.

title: My Birthday & Gameday
description: It was my birthday and gameday for powderpuff. Even though we came up short, I appreciate everything you did for me. I’m so proud of you and so thankful for you.

title: Helping You Move In
description: I helped you move into your first real house. This was such a fun day and felt like a big step for us.

title: For Your Family
description: I went and visited your mom and family for you since you couldn’t make it because of your event. I carried you inside after because you’re my princess.

title: A day with you
description: We went to Marshall’s to buy some goods, stopped at Starbucks, and did more work in your home. You looked stunning in that red dress.

title: My First Car
description: I bought my first ever car all by myself. I remember being so proud of myself this day.

title: Beach Photoshoot
description: We did a photoshoot of you at the beach. I still stare at these photos to this day. I am such a lucky man.

title: Pier 39 With Your Family
description: We took a trip to Pier 39 with your family and had some really good food. Such a warm, fun day together.

title: Road Trip Home
description: We took a road trip to your home. We had to take separate cars but it was fun nonetheless. We also stopped at that Taco Bell where the guy took the worst picture of us ever.

title: Pickleball With Friends
description: We played pickleball with Jasmine and had such a fun time together.

title: Hokkaido Date & Flowers
description: We went on a date to Hokkaido and it was bussdown. We also went to church, and I brought you flowers after your girls night. I love doing stuff for you.

title: 7/11 Slurpees
description: It was 7/11 so we got our quarter slurpees because they charge for the cups. I caught a crazy brain freeze.

title: Pulled Up To Your Work
description: This was the first time I pulled up to your work wearing the best shirt in the world.

title: Five Months
description: Our 5 month. We got Wingstop, did our traditional donut, and decorated my wall with pictures of you. I loved this day.

title: Boardwalk & Pier
description: These days I just thought you looked so beautiful. One day was at the boardwalk and the other was at the pier. I adore you.

title: First Haircut (Learning Curve 😭)
description: I cut your hair for the first time. I felt bad because I didn’t do great and we went to the salon to fix it. We also went to the beach since it was such a pretty day.

title: Dinner at Jasmine’s
description: We had that dinner night at Jasmine’s house. Although it was eventful, I had a lot of fun dressing up and living life with you.

title: Boardwalk With Anthony
description: We took Anthony to the boardwalk. I had a lot of fun and I absolutely adore all of these photos of you.

title: Bowling & Beach Day
description: We went bowling for the first time and we both were not great. I had so much fun — you can hear the little kid in me come out. We also went to the beach just for funsies.

title: Six Months 🤍
description: It was our six month. We went to an Italian restaurant and I felt so happy with you. You surprised me with donuts when I got off work. I felt bad because I had to work, but I loved this day.

title: Redwoods & Home
description: We took another trip to your home. We drove out to see the big redwoods because I had never seen them before — it was for sure an experience. Also miss little man Frank, I hope he's doing alright.

title: Açaí Date
description: We had a small date to the açaí bowl place. They are expensive, but when they get us right, it is definitely worth it.

title: Rush Event & Family
description: It was a rush event. I thought you looked so beautiful so we stopped to take some pictures. After that, we went to go see your family in San Jose and play the guitar.

title: Keysight UGM
description: I had gotten invited to Keysight for their UGM. It was cool and exciting to be in a facility headquarters. I was bummed that the role I did well in the interview process for got canceled.

title: Brunch Date
description: We had a brunch date at Champ’s other job. I really loved these pictures of you.

title: Flowers
description: I surprised you with flowers. I thought you looked very pretty and I couldn’t not take a picture of that smile.

title: AY Photoshoot
description: AY had a photoshoot and my oh my did you look so stunning. I adore you.

title: Mochi Comes Home
description: We brought Mochi to my house for the first time. My housemates brought her in so nicely — except for Warren. He got privileges revoked.

title: Halloween
description: It was Halloween. You did your thing on your costumes and I loved spending the day with you. Next year is gonna be fun!
